Description: WORK IN PROGRESS. This package is for statistics students new to R, RStudio, 
    and associated tools like Quarto. My aim is to help them learn
    by throwing them into the deep end with touchable examples. This package will
    contain code that will generate study guides, homework templates, and presentation
    templates using Quarto documents.This package was born out of my reflections on my own learning journey as a masters 
    student in statistics and inspired by many cool blog posts. 
